partnerDetails.about:
Top quality work and Exceptional service on schedule and within budget

Here at Topa Electrical it’s all about the long game. We’d like to work with you today, in 10 years time and beyond.

Topa Electrical is built around our reputation for ensuring there are no surprises for our clients. We are proud of what we do. We stand behind every job we undertake, from small or large electrical work to complete hassle-free project management. We look after our customers regardless of whether they are small residential jobs or large commercial and industrial refits and new builds.
